d 'SSKAPP': module to compute sample size for the kappa-statistic measure of interrater agreement
d
d  sskapp computes the sample size for the kappa-statistic measure
d of interrater agreement. It is a modification of M. E.
d Reichenheim's sskdlg, published in STB-58 (q.v.) 
d
d KW: utilities
d KW: programming
d
d Requires: Stata version 6.0
d
d Distribution-Date: 20001205
d
d Author: Jan Brogger, University of Bergen, Norway
d Support: email jan.brogger@@med.uib.no
d
f sskapp.ado
f sskapp.hlp
